	<task type="role play">
		<turn type="student">You are an encouraging tutor who helps students improve their English by engaging in role play activities. Let’s engage in a role play activity where I, the student, play the role of a client ordering <GA corr="\0">the</GA> dinner in a restaurant. You, the AI, will be the waiter. Ask me questions about what <WO corr="I would like">would <DMCC corr="I">i</DMCC> like</WO> to order, tell me the dishes of the day and so on.</turn>
		<turn type="chatbot" who="ChatGPT">Great! Let’s start. I’ll be the waiter, and you’ll be the client. Ready?
		Waiter: Good evening! Welcome to our restaurant. Have you dined with us before?
		Waiter: Can I get you started with a drink while you look at the menu?
		(Feel free to respond, and we’ll take it from there!)</turn>
		<turn type="student">Yes please, I would like a bottle of water and a glass of wine</turn>
		<turn type="chatbot" who="ChatGPT">Waiter: Of course! Would you like still or sparkling water? And for the wine, do you prefer red or white?
		Waiter: While I get your drinks, would you like to hear about our specials for tonight?</turn>
		<turn type="student">Ask only one thing</turn>
		<turn type="chatbot" who="ChatGPT">Waiter: Would you like still or sparkling water?</turn>
		<turn type="student"><DMCC corr="Still">still</DMCC> water please</turn>
		<turn type="chatbot" who="ChatGPT">Waiter: Thank you. I'll bring your still water right away.
		Waiter: And for the wine, would you prefer red or white?</turn>
		<turn type="student">White thank you</turn>
		<turn type="chatbot" who="ChatGPT">Waiter: Excellent choice! I'll bring your white wine shortly.
		Waiter: Are you ready to order your food, or would you like a few more minutes?</turn>
		<turn type="student">I am ready</turn>
		<turn type="chatbot" who="ChatGPT">Waiter: Wonderful! What would you like to start with? We have a delicious soup of the day, which is a creamy tomato basil, or you could try our fresh Caesar salad.
		Waiter: What would you prefer?</turn>
		<turn type="student">I would like the soup please</turn> 
		<turn type="chatbot" who="ChatGPT">Waiter: Great choice! The tomato basil soup is one of our favorites.
		Waiter: And for your main course, would you like to try our grilled salmon, the chicken Alfredo pasta, or the vegetarian risotto?</turn>
		<turn type="student">I don’t really enjoy those things, what else do you have?</turn>
		<turn type="chatbot" who="ChatGPT">Waiter: I understand! Let me tell you about a few other options. We also have a juicy steak, a margherita pizza, and a hearty vegetable stir-fry with tofu.
		Waiter: Do any of those sound good to you?</turn>
		<turn type="student">Yes I will go with the juicy steak!</turn>
		<turn type="chatbot" who="ChatGPT">Waiter: Excellent choice! Our steak is cooked to perfection. How would you like it cooked?
		Waiter: And would you like any sides with that? We have mashed potatoes, grilled vegetables, or a side salad.</turn>
		<turn type="student">I like it medium rare, and with mashed potatoes please</turn>
		<turn type="chatbot" who="ChatGPT">Waiter: Perfect, a medium-rare steak with mashed potatoes it is!
		Waiter: I’ll get that order in for you. Is there anything else you’d like to add, maybe a dessert or more wine?</turn>
		<turn type="student">Yes, what <GNN corr="desserts">dessert</GNN> do you have?</turn>
		<turn type="chatbot" who="ChatGPT">Waiter: For dessert, we have a rich chocolate lava cake, a classic crème brûlée, or a light lemon sorbet.
		Waiter: What sounds good to you?</turn>
		<turn type="student">Do you have cheesecake?</turn>
		<turn type="chatbot" who="ChatGPT">Waiter: Yes, we do! Our cheesecake is homemade and comes with a choice of strawberry or blueberry compote.
		Waiter: Would you like to try that?</turn>
		<turn type="student">Sure! With strawberry compote</turn>  
		<turn type="chatbot" who="ChatGPT">Waiter: Excellent choice! A cheesecake with strawberry compote.
		Waiter: I’ll get your order in. Your steak and dessert will be ready shortly.
		Waiter: Is there anything else I can get for you in the meantime?</turn>
		<turn type="student">Yes, some bread for the steak please</turn>
		<turn type="chatbot" who="ChatGPT">Waiter: Of course! I’ll bring some fresh bread right away.
		Waiter: Your meal will be out soon. Enjoy the bread while you wait!</turn>
		<turn type="student">Thank you</turn>
		<turn type="chatbot" who="ChatGPT">Waiter: You’re very welcome! I’ll be right back with your bread. Enjoy!</turn>
